name: The Professor
Lore: 'Protocol droids are programmed to interface with a variety of computer technologies. Quick and precise interpretation can dramatically increase operational efficiency.',
Text: 'Use 3 Force to deploy on your side of the table (free if C-3PO on table). If you have a protocol droid aboard a starship or vehicle in a battle, you may use X Force to reduce the battle damage against you by X (by X + 1 if a Nav Computer character is also aboard).',
